Package org.liris.smartgov.simulator.urban.geo.environment.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistanceCosts
    AStar costs that can be used with GeoNodes and GeoArcs, that uses geographic distance between nodes as the heuristic, and arc lengths as costs.
    EdgeSpot
    A class that represents a spot on an edge.
    GeoArc
    Represents a geographical arc.
    GeoNode
    Represents a geographical node.
    GeoStrTree
    An JTS STRTree (Sort-Tile-Recursive algorithm) wrapper used to compute proximity relations among geo nodes.
